724744f-a.title: Manhattan: West Street - 12th Street (West)
724744f-a.text:
Weat Street, east side, from West 12th (formerly Troy) Street,
opposite Pier 50, North River to Gansevoort Street (Pier 52),
inclusive.
April 18, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
